<td valign="middle" align="left">|[[#Adding-and-removing| Up ]]|</td>
<td valign="middle" align="left">|[[#History-browsing| &gt;&gt; ]]|</td>
<td valign="middle" align="left"> &nbsp; </td>
<td valign="middle" align="left"> &nbsp; </td>
<td valign="middle" align="left"> &nbsp; </td>
<td valign="middle" align="left"> &nbsp; </td>
<td valign="middle" align="left">|[[#Top|Top]]|</td>
