<div id="commit-examples-1"></div>
==== commit examples ====


<hr size="6">
<div id="Committing-to-a-branch"></div>
<table cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" border="0">
<tr><td valign="middle" align="left">|[[#commit-examples| &lt; ]]|</td>
